comment: I'm so frustrated when I don't receive Doraemon's A3 poster at CGV Vinh Long. You can't do that. At first, I thought I had finished watching the movie. But when I finished watching and asked the staff, the staff said it was all gone, but at that time I went in first and didn't have a POS while the person who came in later to watch the show and sat near me had one. I didn't understand and I went out to ask the staff why the other guy came in after me and had a POS that I didn't have. What's the strange business? At first, on the table, I saw a lot of POS showing at 11:50, but the staff didn't give it to me, only 3 copies. So what's wrong? Where is my post? I went out to ask again and they said everything. Meanwhile, everyone has a post but I don't. Why is that? I'm the one who came in quite early. Before the movie started, I went in but didn't have time to come out so I told them all. Then the staff at first didn't give me the post. I asked the manager of cgv to immediately reprimand the ticket counter staff for my mistake.
